    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out this absolute gem. I\u2019m honestly so excited to show it to you\u2014it\u2019s in truly pristine condition and looks just as gorgeous as the day it left the showroom! It's been pampered, garage-kept, and loved every single mile, so you won't find a single scratch or worry here. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
      "price": 43900.0,
