    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been professionally overhauled. This chassis remains structurally pristine with a reinforced subframe and zero evidence of stress fracturing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, while the braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors for superior heat dissipation. This example boasts original paint with consistent micron readings and an interior devoid of bolster wear or pixel degradation in the instrument cluster. A true turn-key specimen for the technical purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
