      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish, entirely free from swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time-capsule' state, featuring supple, unscuffed leather, original protective floor mats, and that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and feature operates exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, it is flawless, supported by a comprehensive service history and strictly garage-kept ownership. This car has never seen rain or snow and has been meticulously maintained by a non-smoking enthusiast. If you are looking for an example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one.",
      "price": 44900.0,
