      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and is ready for a new home. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
